hopobject.body: I've just graduated methocarbamol webmd Don't be surprised if when you are rushed to a the hospital with a heart condition that you are not treated by a nurse. The days of talking with your Doctor just got decreased. You may be able to leave a note with the nurse but actually seeing the Doctor won't be the norm. Personally this kind of "change" I didn't want or need. I will use my vote to chop off as many heads over this as possible. Seems Dems. are first in line.
